sequenceDiagram
    participant EvalHub as eval-hub Service
    participant Adapter as Garak Adapter Pod
    participant Sidecar as eval-hub Sidecar<br/>(localhost HTTP)
    participant KFP as KFP API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant SDGModel as SDG Model<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Target as Target Model<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Judge as Judge Model<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Attacker as Attacker Model<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MLflow as MLflow<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over EvalHub,Adapter: Flow 1: Simple Mode Scan
    EvalHub->>Adapter: Create K8s Job<br/>(JobSpec via ConfigMap mount)
    Adapter->>Sidecar: Status: INITIALIZING<br/>(HTTP plaintext)
    Adapter->>Adapter: Resolve config, build command
    Adapter->>Sidecar: Status: RUNNING_EVALUATION
    Adapter->>Target: Garak probes (subprocess)<br/>POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token, TLS 1.2+
    Target-->>Adapter: Model responses
    Adapter->>Adapter: Parse results (JSONL/AVID)<br/>Compute ASR/TBSA metrics
    Adapter->>Sidecar: Status: POST_PROCESSING
    Adapter->>OCI: Upload scan artifacts<br/>Auth: Registry creds, TLS 1.2+
    Adapter->>MLflow: Log metrics & artifacts<br/>Auth: Bearer Token, TLS 1.2+
    Adapter->>Sidecar: Final results + Status: COMPLETE

    Note over EvalHub,Adapter: Flow 2: KFP Mode Scan
    EvalHub->>Adapter: Create K8s Job<br/>(JobSpec via ConfigMap mount)
    Adapter->>Sidecar: Status: INITIALIZING
    Adapter->>KFP: Submit 6-step pipeline<br/>Auth: SA Token, TLS 1.2+
    KFP-->>Adapter: Pipeline run ID

    Note over KFP,S3: KFP Pipeline Steps
    KFP->>S3: Step 1: validate<br/>Auth: AWS IAM
    KFP->>S3: Step 2: resolve_taxonomy<br/>Auth: AWS IAM
    KFP->>SDGModel: Step 3: sdg_generate<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    SDGModel-->>KFP: Generated adversarial prompts
    KFP->>S3: Step 4: prepare_prompts<br/>Upload normalized prompts<br/>Auth: AWS IAM
    KFP->>Target: Step 5: garak_scan<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Target-->>KFP: Scan results
    KFP->>S3: Step 6: write_kfp_outputs<br/>Upload results<br/>Auth: AWS IAM

    Adapter->>KFP: Poll run status<br/>Auth: SA Token
    KFP-->>Adapter: Run complete
    Adapter->>S3: Download results<br/>Auth: AWS IAM
    Adapter->>Sidecar: Final results + Status: COMPLETE

    Note over Adapter,Attacker: Flow 3: Intents-Based Risk Assessment
    Adapter->>SDGModel: Generate adversarial prompts<br/>from harm taxonomy<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    SDGModel-->>Adapter: SDG output
    Adapter->>Target: Garak CAS scan<br/>(multi-probe pipeline)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Adapter->>Judge: MulticlassJudge<br/>score responses<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Adapter->>Attacker: TAP attack model<br/>jailbreak generation<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Adapter->>Attacker: TAP evaluator<br/>jailbreak scoring<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Target-->>Adapter: Responses
    Judge-->>Adapter: Scores
    Attacker-->>Adapter: Attack results
    Adapter->>Adapter: Aggregate by (intent, stub)<br/>Compute ASR per intent
